article.headline: Mount St. Mary's, Md. 78, Quinnipiac 73
article.story: EMMITSBURG, Md. (AP) -- Chris Vann scored a game-high 28 points and grabbed six rebounds, and Mount St. Mary's defeated Quinnipiac 78-73 Thursday night. Mychal Kearse added 18 points and grabbed a game-high 7 rebounds for Mount St. Mary's (2-6). Van Crafton scored a team-high 23 points for Quinnipiac (2-5).
